d:
Previously this prompter went and hid/geofenced all their content at the end of November 2025; now their stuff is visible to me again and I don't know whether it's by their own willingness to stop geofencing or because Pixiv is finally taking my non-US/EU location preference seriously.

That means I got to re-encode almost every ugoira in .webm then downstep to .webp in Pixiv submission chronological order so this gallery doesn't look so empty. (Torrent will feature both .gif and .webm lossless versions as well.) 2026 already looks strong for this prompter (if they seem to be abandoning their latex model in favor of something more pantyhose-proficient) and will be covered in a separate, hopefully monthly-updating gallery.

Support the prompter: https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/116376257
